This was a Project series placed by a YouTuber Codebasics, within which he mentioned a true life progress in making associate 60 minutes report for associate 60 minutes person during a globe company AtliQ. He showed up from loading the information, to cleaning/transforming the information, learning concerning the KPIs required by the 60 minutes person of the corporate.
Problem Statement
The problem for the corporate was that they were during a hybrid mode of working i.e some staff are coming back to workplace to figure and a few are working from home. They needed insights on the Attendance/Presence of the staff for his or her past three months of information.
